  "instructions": [
    "Heat the oil in a large clay pot over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until it is lightly browned.",
    "Add the grated carrot and cook for 2 minutes.",
    "Add the green beans and cook until they are tender.",
    "Add the curry powder, garam masala, and salt, and stir well.",
    "Add the basmati rice and stir to coat the rice with the spice mixture.",
    "Add the water and bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce the heat to low, cover the pot, and simmer for 20 minutes.",
    "Turn off the heat and let the biryani rest for 5 minutes.",
    "Fluff the biryani with a fork and serve hot."
  ],
